content:
[[iftags 组件]]
使用方法请参见[[[the-alleys-other-goif|指南]]].
[[/iftags]]

[[iftags -组件]]
[[module CSS]]
.scp-woi-block {
    border-left: #000 1px solid;
    border-right: #000 1px solid;
    border-top: #000 1px solid;
    border-bottom: none;
    background-color: #fcfcfc;
    color: #000000;
}

.scp-woi-title {
    color: #292929;
    font-weight: bolder;
    border-bottom: #000 1px solid;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #C2EBF2, #7AC0CC);
    padding-top: 0.3em;
    padding-right: 1em;
    padding-left: 1em;
    padding-bottom: 1em;
}

.scp-woi-caption {
    background-color: none;
    padding-top: 0.5em;
    padding-right: 2em;
    padding-left: 2em;
    padding-bottom: 1em;
}

.scp-woi-image {
    background-color: #fff;
    border: #000 1px solid;
}

.scp-woi-forum-0 {
    background-color: none;
    border-top: #000 1px solid;
    padding-top: 1em;
    padding-right: 1em;
    padding-left: 1em;
    padding-bottom: 0.5em;
}
[[/module]]


[[div class="scp-woi-block"]]
[[div class="scp-woi-title"]]
,,[{$category}],,
[[size 180%]]{$title}[[/size]]
[[table style="margin: auto; border-collapse:collapse; width: 100%"]]
[[row]]
[[cell style="text-align: left; border: 0px solid; padding: 0 0 0;"]]
**作者:** {$writer}{$color}
[[/cell]]
[[cell style="text-align: right; border: 0px solid; padding: 0 0 0;"]]
**日期:** {$date}
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[/table]]
[[/div]]
@@@@
[[=]]
[[image {$image} style="width: 70%; border: #000 0.5px solid;"]]
[[/=]]

[[div class="scp-woi-caption"]]
[[/iftags]]
